RT @getachew_temare: #Ethiopia’s conflict with the northern #Tigray region has put civilians beyond the reach of aid agencies, raising fear…

before other sleepy town
become hallowed ground
killer
     angeled by
stupidity
#poem #civilwar

fighting their to decide
the human right to 
measure human life
as thing
     like peanut, be sold
at market

and speaking
   of market let
me set out my stall
of rich
     memorabilia from
these less wondrous moments 

#poem #civilwar

then across the pond
to town of shoes, shoes
necessary for 
  Johnny to
march home
            again

but after this three-day wrangle
over some Pennsylvania town
too few Billies or
Johnnies ever
march again

#poem #civilwar

or Naseby: that one 
about man on a horse
two men in fact
believing 
        will of
God their
own discourse
and style
   of hair, of course,
whether curled and careless
or cut morally severe

#poem #civilwar

forty-thousand dead by fall
of night (most drowned or
chopped in half or
skull glave-smashed)

made the fight
a bit pointless
since rose cause
red 
   by fall
of night itself
bled white

#poem #civilwar

CIVIL WAR

let's have
a civil war
as we stoop
to folly

two sides
both playing
at home
brother
versus brother

what
could be more jolly

at Towton the steely ranks
of horticulturists met
to decide
   definitively 
which rose was best 

#poem #civilwar
